high_descs: Go to the round black table in the left corner.
Pick up the gray knife.
Turn around and go to the counter on the right of the sink.
Slice the red tomato on the right.
Turn around and go to the small black table in the right corner.
Put the gray knife on the table in front of the chef's knife.
Go back to the counter next to the sink.
Pick up one slice of tomato.
Turn around and go to the microwave above the stove on the right.
Microwave the slice of tomato and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the small black table on the right.
Place the heated tomato slice in between other tomatoes.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the large round black table.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the table.
Turn around and move toward the counter top that is on the left  of the sink.
There are two tomatoes.  Slice the tomato that is on the right.
Turn around and move toward the corner opposite the round table.  There is a small, black two shelf stand.
Place the knife on the stand by the lettuce and other large knife.
Turn around and return to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the tomato slice off of the counter.
Turn to the right and move to the stove.
There is a microwave above the stove.  Cook the tomato.  Remove the tomato from the microwave.
Turn around, and move across the room toward the small black stand in the corner with the two  shelves.
Place the cooked tomato on top of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Cook a tomato in the microwave to be placed on the small black shelf.

high_descs: move left to the table
pick up the knife
turn around to the sink
slice the tomato on the sink
turn around to the shelf
drop the knife on the shelf
turn around to the sink
pick up the tomato slice
turn around to the oven
cook the tomato in it
turn around to the shelf
drop the cooked tomato on it
anns.task_desc: place a cooked tomato slice on the shelf
